rmal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efcd3ca686d1a033e4c03609f94587f13964cdd","tid":1218933,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcc9b34bb11d4c631ea74f8b3a26662f39aece1c","tid":1218933,"uid":131843,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/14/MUOL68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2FMUOL68.png&h=85f851e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncomment有印尼示威經驗人士咁講，話佢地係咁做，係咪真？<br />\n如果係，應該每人袋支旅行裝牙膏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:07:03.000Z","msg":"推下先，等證實"},{"pid":"1805168bf0d121fcfc8e7e0855a47d64d2954597","tid":1218933,"uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:13:30.000Z","msg":"尋晚睇reddit 見到下面呢個post, 2000 up vote 既.  講點對應tear gas<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1 half water, 1 half Maalox, put it &icirc;n a squirt bottle, clean your face regularily. You should be ok, maybe a bit White on the face due to Maalox. Face mask for painting, ski google, bike helmet ventilated and you are good to go and survive. Source: been &icirc;n a lot of clashes, &icirc;n Rom&acirc;nia, &icirc;n during 10.08.18 Good luck, take care.<br />\nEdit: you can spray it in your mouth and nose also, Better have some water in instead of tear gas, can be applied prior to gas actions, it will set a protective layer on the skin and soft tissue &icirc;n your nostrils. Regular bottles for window cleaning (sprays mist instead of jet) make a loop from a thin rope, have the bottle across your body so you have free hands and you don't lose it.<br />\nEDIT 2: thanks a lot for the gold, I am a bit annoyed that my first gold is for a comment on how not getting you ass kicked by police, when you are not violent. This shit happened &icirc;n my country also (RO) and the government is trying to cover up the violent and brutal reaction of riot police."},{"pid":"a0c45e762177a43c7f9c4e386f453881ce3c242a","tid":1218933,"uid":260460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:16:02.000Z","msg":"9gag係香港人整"},{"pid":"2558b9e6fd9af916c7216c447751754b8753ace0","tid":1218933,"uid":62654,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"記者twitter都有 都好多人retweet同like<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MadNOom.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMadNOom.png&h=05eafa1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ramyinocencio/status/1138978532640485377?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Framyinocencio%2Fstatus%2F1138978532640485377%3Fs%3D21&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=742f2ad6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Framyinocencio%2Fstatus%2F1138978532640485377%3Fs%3D21&h=dbb6b542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ramyinocencio/status/1138978532640485377?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"9b6a4a44c7fccd8db7c05d2f376a2ed606e1965b","tid":1218933,"uid":202309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcc9b34bb11d4c631ea74f8b3a26662f39aece1c","tid":1218933,"uid":131843,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/14/MUOL68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2FMUOL68.png&h=85f851e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncomment有印尼示威經驗人士咁講，話佢地係咁做，係咪真？<br />\n如果係，應該每人袋支旅行裝牙膏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"26659f16c1aeac463a4005f6ee7d329859a5cc5d","tid":1218933,"uid":58318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:52:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02b051f05554fbe9c4d9cad0e942e7942cc823e8","tid":1218933,"uid":258907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:53:27.000Z","msg":"老細係香港人 係唔同啲"},{"pid":"f9f3ca2438996bda013064b71a2e1c0a9b4468ba","tid":1218933,"uid":23156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcc9b34bb11d4c631ea74f8b3a26662f39aece1c","tid":1218933,"uid":131843,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/14/MUOL68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2FMUOL68.png&h=85f851e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncomment有印尼示威經驗人士咁講，話佢地係咁做，係咪真？<br />\n如果係，應該每人袋支旅行裝牙膏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:53:53.000Z","msg":"發夢當日鬼佬攝記有教呢個方法"},{"pid":"bdd0841c2b4f84eac807c7e18a074592eda6efaa","tid":1218933,"uid":123050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:08:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有關行政機關濫用權力</strong></span><br />\n二戰末期，納粹德國敗局已現，佛斯曼醫師、門格勒、拉舍爾三人的命運也隨著戰爭快速流轉。1945年時，拉舍爾因犯罪而被處死，和被他殺死的許多人一樣，葬身於達豪集中營裡。而門格勒假扮成一般士兵，躲過追緝後流亡到南美洲，直到1979年在巴西意外溺斃後才被確認身分。而始終堅持人性的佛斯曼醫師則在戰火中存活了下來，1945年時游過易北河後向美軍投降，戰後以泌尿科醫師的身份默默地生活著。在惡魔的年代結束之際，三名醫師分別擁來了他們各自的結局&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg&h=327c7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上圖：將人浸入冰水當中，藉此研究在低溫下人體的反應；左下圖：故意讓小孩感染結核菌，並切除腋下的淋巴腺，測試人體的免疫力；右圖：紐倫堡審判中，對卡爾&middot;勃蘭特（Karl Brandt）醫師的審判，他被控同意並參與非人道實驗和其他戰爭罪行，最後被判<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>絞刑</strong></span>。<br />\n用屍體換來的規範－紐倫堡守則<br />\n堆積如山的屍體、骨瘦如柴的幸存者，那些泯滅人性的實驗震撼了全世界。1948年在紐倫堡進行的醫師審判，被告的醫師之中，不乏知名的科學家，如施靈（Klaus Karl Schilling）曾是國際瘧疾研究聯盟的成員，戰時卻刻意讓一千多名囚犯感染瘧疾來進行科學研究。科學家在戰爭期間荒唐的行徑，讓美國醫師里昂&middot;亞歷山大（Leo Alexander）動筆起草人體實驗中應有的道德規範，也就是今日我們熟知的「紐倫堡公約」，寫明了醫師在任何情況之下，都不得傷害受試者（除非受試者就是醫師本人）。而1964年在芬蘭舉辦的全球醫師大會更提出「赫爾辛基宣言（The Declaration of Helsinki）」，說明了受試者有絕對的權利了解實驗內容，保障了受試者「知情同意」的權益。數十年的努力之下，美國和其他國家都誓言杜絕非人道的臨床實驗，全世界都認為這種惡魔般的人體實驗不會再出現了。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行政機關濫權者請接受審判</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"800c90e5c9d39ef1839c0054240efb43f9d3b215","tid":1218933,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:10:40.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c5060843a25739d31a613754982ee508f9e099","tid":1218933,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:17:16.000Z","msg":"睇親都覺得好warm好愛香港人"},{"pid":"83095de4bde20839110e1ed65a1ad8d9e422daae","tid":1218933,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:24:03.000Z","msg":"唔係想捉你字蚤，但係以牙還牙同百倍奉還好似係互相衝突，以牙還牙係&quot;一倍奉還&quot;嘅意思，有冇其他更好嘅用字？"},{"pid":"6514212787debdc72dffd9641ec56212fc5bee1b","tid":1218933,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4c6b59199878ffe004cfb6adef66a4dbf644198","tid":1218933,"uid":244243,"like":12,"dislike":11,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:09:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"sorry, 唔記得quote, 係覆緊呢個回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033197b2712c2daa1282c15fe267a47355a524dd","tid":1218933,"uid":131843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f3ca2438996bda013064b71a2e1c0a9b4468ba","tid":1218933,"uid":23156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcc9b34bb11d4c631ea74f8b3a26662f39aece1c","tid":1218933,"uid":131843,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/14/MUOL68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2FMUOL68.png&h=85f851e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncomment有印尼示威經驗人士咁講，話佢地係咁做，係咪真？<br />\n如果係，應該每人袋支旅行裝牙膏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:53:53.000Z","msg":"發夢當日鬼佬攝記有教呢個方法"},"citedBy